<%= render :partial => "sidebar" %>

<div class="content" style="float: left; width: 40em;">
  <h2 class="wiki-title"><%= h(@wiki_page.pretty_title) %> (Editing)</h2>
  <div id="wiki-view">
  </div>
  <% form_tag(:action => "update") do %>
    <%= hidden_field "wiki_page", "title", :value => @wiki_page.title %>
    <%= render :partial => 'edit_buttons' %>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div style="float: left; margin-left: 5em; width: 15em;">
  <h4>Reference</h4>
  <pre>
A paragraph.

Followed by another.

h4. A header

* List item 1
* List item 2
* List item 3

Linebreaks are important between lists, 
headers, and paragraphs.

URLs are automatically linked: http://www.google.com

A [[wiki link]] (underscores are not needed).

A {{post link}}.

<a href="/help/dtext">Read more</a>.
  </pre>
</div>

